{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/actix/actix-web/issues/1680","repository_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/actix/actix-web","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/actix/actix-web/issues/1680/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/actix/actix-web/issues/1680/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/actix/actix-web/issues/1680/events","html_url":"https://github.com/actix/actix-web/issues/1680","id":701426835,"node_id":"MDU6SXNzdWU3MDE0MjY4MzU=","number":1680,"title":"Missing v3 migration note on req.app_data::<T>() ?","user":{"login":"staninprague","id":3834343,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjM4MzQzNDM=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/3834343?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/staninprague","html_url":"https://github.com/staninprague","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/staninprague/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/staninprague/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/staninprague/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/staninprague/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/staninprague/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/staninprague/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/staninprague/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/staninprague/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/staninprague/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"labels":[{"id":1298345548,"node_id":"MDU6TGFiZWwxMjk4MzQ1NTQ4","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/actix/actix-web/labels/C-docs","name":"C-docs","color":"b9d644","default":false,"description":"Category: docs"}],"state":"closed","locked":false,"assignee":null,"assignees":[],"milestone":null,"comments":2,"created_at":"2020-09-14T21:07:53Z","updated_at":"2020-09-14T21:34:51Z","closed_at":"2020-09-14T21:26:38Z","author_association":"NONE","type":null,"active_lock_reason":null,"sub_issues_summary":{"total":0,"completed":0,"percent_completed":0},"issue_dependencies_summary":{"blocked_by":0,"total_blocked_by":0,"blocking":0,"total_blocking":0},"body":"Thank you for version 3!\r\n\r\nAfter migration I noticed that for my app data of type ServerData that I used to retrieve in middleware as:\r\n\r\n```\r\nlet app_data = req.app_data::<ServerData>();\r\n```\r\n\r\nVersion 3 newly returns None when version 2 used to retrieve app data.\r\n\r\nInstance method documentation is:\r\n```\r\n/// Counterpart to [`HttpRequest::app_data`](../struct.HttpRequest.html#method.app_data).\r\n```\r\n\r\nHttpRequest::app_data documentation points to the root cause:\r\n\r\n```\r\n    /// If `App::data` was used to store object, use `Data<T>`:\r\n    ///\r\n    /// ```rust,ignore\r\n    /// let opt_t = req.app_data::<Data<T>>();\r\n```\r\n\r\nFor my code, this is a runtime breaking change from v2 and it would be nice to have a migration point:\r\n\r\nChange:\r\n\r\n```\r\nlet app_data = req.app_data::<T>();\r\n```\r\nTo\r\n```\r\nlet app_data = req.app_data::<Data<T>>();\r\n```\r\n\r\n* Rust Version (I.e, output of `rustc -V`):\r\n1.46.0\r\n* Actix Web Version:\r\n3.0.1\r\n","closed_by":{"login":"robjtede","id":3316789,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjMzMTY3ODk=","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/3316789?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/robjtede","html_url":"https://github.com/robjtede","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/robjtede/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/robjtede/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/robjtede/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/robjtede/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/robjtede/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/robjtede/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/robjtede/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/u